org.lexgrid.extension.valuedomain.admin
Class LoadValueDomain

java.lang.Object
  org.lexgrid.extension.valuedomain.admin.LoadValueDomain

public class LoadValueDomain
extends java.lang.Object

Imports the source file, provided in LexGrid canonical format, to the LexBIG repository. 

 Example: java org.lexgrid.extension.valuedomain.admin.LoadValueDomain
   -in,--input <uri> URI or path specifying location of the source file
   -v, --validate <int> Perform validation of the candidate
         resource without loading data.  
         Supported levels of validation include:
         0 = Verify document is well-formed
         1 = Verify document is valid
 
 Example: java -Xmx512m -cp lgRuntime.jar
  org.lexgrid.extension.valuedomain.admin.LoadValueDomain -in "file:///path/to/file.xml" -v 0
